SUMMARY OF H.R. 5382,

Commercial Space Launch Amendments Act of 2004

Introduced  by  Mr.  Rohrabacher  (CA)  and  co-sponsored  by  Mr.  Boehlert  (NY)  and

Mr. Gordon (TN)

Key features of the Act include:

