Mr.  RUTAN.  And  if  you  are  afraid  to  fly  it,  you  never  learn  any-

Mr.  BARTLETT.  That  is  right.  You  know,  and  people  who  don’t
come  from  a  science  background  have  a  lot  of  trouble  under-

thing.

